# -- $0: MINIMAL LOCAL GLOSSARY --
# Required: every .cortex artifact must be locally self-contained.
# Sigil | Name | Type | Risk | Cognitive Layer | Description
# IDN   | identity   | attrs      | B | Semantic       | Agent identity descriptor
# KNW   | knw        | attrs      | M | Semantic       | TODO: needs_review
# AXM   | axiom      | cuerpo     | H | Prefrontal     | Non-negotiable principles
# LIM   | limit      | attrs      | M | Prefrontal     | Hard limits and boundaries
# AUD   | aud        | attrs      | M | Semantic       | TODO: needs_review
# RSK   | rsk        | attrs      | M | Semantic       | TODO: needs_review
# FCS   | focus      | attrs      | H | Working        | Default attention anchor
# OBJ   | objective  | attrs      | H | Working        | Standing objectives
# WRK   | wrk        | attrs      | M | Semantic       | TODO: needs_review
# LNG   | lesson     | attrs      | M | Episodic       | Behavioral lessons
# DESC  | description | cuerpo     | B | Semantic       | Agent description and style
# ERR   | err        | attrs      | M | Semantic       | TODO: needs_review
# ARQX  | artifact   | attrs      | B | Semantic       | ArqUX artifact metadata
#
# Types:
# attrs = canonical type
# bloque = canonical type
# cuerpo = canonical type
# attrs-pos = canonical type
# relación = canonical type
#
# Micro-glossary:
# cur=current pln=planned fut=future blk=blocked
# min=minimum rec=recovery wrk=work full=full
# ok=success fail=failure part=partial


